name: Lista Appuntamenti
query:
SELECT
`tabPatient Appointment`.appointment_date AS "Data::100",
`tabPatient Appointment`.appointment_time AS "Orario::100",
`tabPatient Appointment`.patient_name AS "Paziente::300",
`tabItem`.item_name AS "Servizio::200",
`tabPatient`.idr_patient_phone_no AS "Telefono::200",
physician AS "Medico::200"
FROM `tabPatient Appointment`
JOIN `tabItem` ON `tabItem`.name=`tabPatient Appointment`.idr_appointment_type
JOIN `tabPatient` ON `tabPatient`.patient_name=`tabPatient Appointment`.patient_name
